title: Exquisite! Huge Balcony, Heat is Paid, Close to Shopping!
posting_body: ['Contact info:', 'Mike Miller | The Apartment Resource |', 'show contact info', '3BR/2Ba - Just 2 Miles to Rosedale, Impressive Amenities!', 'Dale St N, Roseville, MN', '$2160/mo', 'KEY FEATURES', 'Sq Footage:', '1260 sqft.', 'Bedroom:', '3', 'Bathroom:', '2', 'Parking:', '2 Dedicated', 'Lease Duration:', '12 Months', 'Deposit:', '$500', 'Pets Policy:', 'Cats & Dogs OK', 'Laundry:', 'Laundry Facility On-Site', 'Property Type:', 'Apartment', 'DESCRIPTION', 'Located in a gorgeous residential neighborhood of Roseville, MN.', 'Offering fantastic 1, 2 and 3 bedroom apartment homes with airy kitchens, balconies.', 'heated underground parking, billiard room and fitness center.', 'Enjoy the walking paths nearby or Rosedale Shopping Center is just 2 miles away.', 'Our impeccable landscaping and beautiful grounds are sure to impress.', 'We have everything you are looking for in an apartment home', 'and we are pet friendly too!', 'Equal Housing Opportunity.', 'Prices and availability are subject to change.', 'Photos may not represent exact unit.', 'COMMUNITY FEATURES', 'Close to Shopping, Restaurants and Downtown', 'Trash chutes/recycling', 'On Bus Line', 'Car wash', '24-Hour Emergency Maintenance', 'Located in Residential Neighborhood', 'On Site Management Office', 'BBQ Grilling Area', 'Balcony/Patio on All Homes', 'Fitness Center', 'Elevator in Building', 'Controlled Building Access', 'Community Room', 'Monitoring Cameras', 'Heated Underground Parking', 'Laundry on each floor', 'Pets Welcome!', 'Contact info:', 'Mike Miller', 'The Apartment Resource', 'show contact info']
